Localization.Name: Wikelo Emporium Bust
Localization.Description: Hello, human neighbor. I am Wikelo and now live in your human system of Stanton. Have many things if you would like to come visit. Can make too. If not, I understand. Enjoy this gift from me.\n\nBye.
